PrecisAppointment of KATHY MILSOM of King, Ontario, to be a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years; and designation of KATHY MILSOM to be Chairperson of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years.
